Ross Enamait - Infinite Intensity (2005)
----------------------------------------

TITLE: Infinite Intensity: The Revolution is Here
AUTHOR: Ross Enamait
YEAR: 2005
LANGUAGE: English
FORMAT: PDF

SYNOPSIS: Efficient, intense and effective training are the ways to describe this book. The routines in this guide will address all aspects of fitness. If you are looking for a quick fix, do yourself a favor and look elsewhere, if however you are looking for a challenge then you will find what you need here.
